text: Nadja Tiller ( March 16, 1929 -21 February 2023) is an Austrian actress. She was one of the most popular Austrian actresses and was well known during the 1950s and 1960s. She was born in Vienna. Her best known roles were Ich suche Dich (1955) and Rosemary (1958).Nadja Tiller wird 80 Jahre alt (9 March 2009) She won the Miss Austria competition in 1949. ==References== Category:1929 births Category:Living people Category:Austrian movie actors Category:Austrian television actors Category:Austrian stage actors Category:Austrian models Category:Actors from Vienna
